<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٦١ ... سُورَةُ الصَّفِّ ... آياتها ١٤ ... مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبَّحَ لِلَّهِ}</span> ... نَزَّهَ اللهَ عَمَّا لَا يَلِيقُ بِجَلَالِهِ سُبْحَانَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَبُرَ مَقْتًا}</span> ... عَظُمَ بُغْضًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَفًّا}</span> ... صَافِّينَ صَفًّا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّرْصُوصٌ}</span> ... مُتَرَاصٌّ مُحْكَمٌ لَا فُرْجَةَ فِيهِ، وَلَا يَنْفُذُ فِيهِ العَدُوُّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَاغُوا}</span> ... عَدَلُوا عَنِ الحَقِّ، مَعَ عِلْمِهِمْ بِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَزَاغَ اللَّهُ قُلُوبَهُمْ}</span> ... صَرَفَهَا عَنْ قَبُولِ الحَقِّ؛ جَزَاءً عَلَى زَيْغِهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيَّ}</span> ... لِمَا جَاءَ قَبْلِي.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْبَيِّنَاتِ}</span> ... بِالآيَاتِ الوَاضِحَاتِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَنْ أَظْلَمُ}</span> ... لَا أَحَدَ أَشَدُّ ظُلْمًا، وَعُدْوَانًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{افْتَرَى}</span> ... اخْتَلَقَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُدْعَى إِلَى الْإِسْلَامِ}</span> ... يُدْعَى إِلَى الدُّخُولِ فِي الإِسْلَامِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُورَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... الحَقَّ الَّذِي جَاءَ بِهِ الرَّسُولُ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِأَفْوَاهِهِمْ}</span> ... بِأَقْوَالِهِمُ الكَاذِبَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُتِمُّ نُورِهِ}</span> ... مُظْهِرٌ الحَقَّ بِإِتْمَامِ دِينِهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِيُظْهِرَهُ}</span> ... لِيُعْلِيَهُ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الدِّينِ كُلِّهِ}</span> ... الأَدْيَانِ المُخَالِفَةِ كُلِّهَا.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأُخْرَى}</span> ... وَنِعْمَةٌ أُخْرَى لَكُمْ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>